{"tid":1494971,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[live]跟住河內人去河內，「真」美食之旅","createTime":"2019-08-22T00:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:02:13.000Z","uid":8203,"like":5,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee57125c07afd530fa0d123d9afbbb39949cf9e","tid":1494971,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:42:04.000Z","msg":"首先容許我向各位講聲對唔住！<br />\n係香港最危急既時刻我無係香港陪大家共患難<br />\n見呢排比較少遊記去越南，尤其河內<br />\n我大概兩年前識我女朋友，佢同我都最中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好自豪自己上三代都住河內<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似日本既江戸っ子咁<br />\n河內係一個美食之都 但係當地人先去既鋪頭<br />\n相信無當地人帶路就好難知道<br />\n就等我向大家揭露河內既平民美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqFa4ev.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqFa4ev.png&h=214eeebb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGbYtGg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGbYtGg.png&h=5928fd64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成田既廁所 全個室 幾特別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZkZWfmA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZkZWfmA.png&h=270e6240&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3vyhz1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3vyhz1.png&h=766b676c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQVVvU8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQVVvU8.png&h=bfb903a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次坐A320neo <br />\n唔夠兩年機齡但係一日可以跑兩年<br />\n架機已經幾殘下<br />\ncabin crew仲要過半係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n差唔多起飛<br />\n我地五個鐘後再見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ab8900a2fa4b988ba92ec26332ef53c58611fe58","tid":1494971,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:43:07.000Z","msg":"屌 係a321neo先岩<br />\n<br />\na320neo坐過快運"},{"pid":"0cf37adf4b570cb60fdab365aa2180bb4dc94928","tid":1494971,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:45:58.000Z","msg":"又有錯字 係一日跑兩轉<br />\n<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一打"},{"pid":"01d3c0d295457334f1dd10d314ecc24962f7d39c","tid":1494971,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:58:05.000Z","msg":"入正題plz"},{"pid":"84c40a4a6e77110b6382636793e3e73348883429","tid":1494971,"uid":129586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"太早入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名先"},{"pid":"efc453411cce7fb08c6bd49925766e34e22860a1","tid":1494971,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最近係河內同胡志明玩過桃色之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf4088821f2352526258430dede5d041fd70107","tid":1494971,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:56:37.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<br />\n越南妹女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e52c564f1790fcb5c562051cc976b42e4e711cb","tid":1494971,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ffaef4f6501732bb15c44f929e5f878b06ef1d50","tid":1494971,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"157f0d790b12d6aa6a1778d5b20a0d9dd0f41b69","tid":1494971,"uid":41961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /